{"tid":684503,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[Live]米蘭行路去威尼斯的三百幾","createTime":"2018-05-30T14:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T16:09:34.000Z","uid":188708,"like":49,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"8c6e66ce4390c3d651330012c388247fd256d38f","tid":684503,"uid":188708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T14:56:14.000Z","msg":"米蘭去威尼斯話近唔近，話遠唔遠，如果相信Google大神嘅指路行高速公路，大概兩日半就可以行完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/30/225523_fd4a73913a78fc9f2f0061010b36334a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F30%2F225523_fd4a73913a78fc9f2f0061010b36334a.png&h=d9477039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當然實際上就無可能三日啦...Live之前講幾句真心話先，順便交代吓點解想行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一路好欣賞好多人講得出做得到，好有決心去達成目標，而自己就成日婆婆媽媽唔敢去馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上個月去海邊嘅時候，為咗趕得切睇日落，一路狂奔幾百米，就係為咗睇到鹹蛋黃喺山邊落，睇住水嘅顏色連埋個景慢慢變暗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰吓嘅感覺係：好耐無試過咁單純去做一樣嘢，而且想做就去做。<br />\n<br />\n適逢自己喺米蘭Exchange做廢青一年，又有少少假期<br />\n<br />\n唔想自己再廢落去，難得腦裡面閃過呢個念頭，就覺得唔得，唔可以令自己後悔，成廿一歲人，要做返件實現自己嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n威尼斯，曾經係世界上最富裕嘅城邦，喺中世紀以後，呢個地方發明自己嘅規則，好多人去搜尋機會，追尋夢想。行去呢個地方，就好似有種圓夢嘅感覺咁。<br />\n<br />\n- - -<br />\n<br />\n如果要為呢個旅程改個名，我會幻想自己係世界上最出名嘅意大利人&mdash;Mario，係呀紅色衫水管佬，過五關斬六將咁前往城堡拯救公主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n公主我就無喇，城堡都好似無，唯有當終點威尼斯嘅聖馬可教堂係Boss城堡，由米蘭出發，行路去威尼斯，拯救我嘅夢想。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0131dcf90f4f58fc8426c3bb862a1ed4ec3d2ca","tid":684503,"uid":54012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T14:58:04.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"27cdba9a798395d9bd3519bb904cdd9b1549318a","tid":684503,"uid":188708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:02:43.000Z","msg":"喺連登做CD-Rom咁耐第一次出Post，有咩得罪各位巴絲屌得細力啲<br />\n<br />\nUpdate頻率會參考東京行去京都嘅Moyashi巴，除非有啲咩特別嘢，否則都係一日一次或者兩次（因為時差，如果每日都行完先Po，個Po應該永遠潛水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 盡量Lunch或者嘅Break嘅時候都會Up一Update）<br />\n<br />\n暫時個Plan係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/30/230128_6652e7f327ac8621160398576f0fab0f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F30%2F230128_6652e7f327ac8621160398576f0fab0f.png&h=cfc1afed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/30/230052_661a64c33ab8b6aa91badc9803f0d2ea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F30%2F230052_661a64c33ab8b6aa91badc9803f0d2ea.png&h=635fea88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n諗住一日行30-50k不等（因為平嘅住宿好難搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）如果順利，中間會唞一日，應該十日可以到威尼斯"},{"pid":"d9cf0cf964edddba94251400bf6da21cb7100ef5","tid":684503,"uid":188708,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:05:23.000Z","msg":"屌個標題打漏咗<br />\n係三百幾公里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日係第一日，依家仲喺路上，預計今晚十點（香港時間凌晨四點）會到Bergamo市郊嘅住宿 到時再Update 遲咗起行要趕路<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c941d05c57e2b61a18ed88a6f855218b6bfbf571","tid":684503,"uid":79662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:05:39.000Z","msg":"巴打我都住米蘭啵 <br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  坐火車都4個鍾"},{"pid":"97c12a604c928844804d71741b114d8f368cbabb","tid":684503,"uid":30729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:07:44.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ecbd9a0994045de5501ca2a8ae2ada043948497","tid":684503,"uid":112651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:08:11.000Z","msg":"想做就去做，已經係一個夢想"},{"pid":"9ef01fe20117972f4fd46253b8c34e8764437cc6","tid":684503,"uid":75123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:08:51.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"bd677a4b90b8f75a1abd86346ca6c80f67fcab20","tid":684503,"uid":188708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c941d05c57e2b61a18ed88a6f855218b6bfbf571","tid":684503,"uid":79662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:05:39.000Z","msg":"巴打我都住米蘭啵 <br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  坐火車都4個鍾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:10:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Exchange咁耐幾乎無遇過香港人 遊客除外<br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350f6718c074a172458906bced59f7fc791b9be0","tid":684503,"uid":188708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:25:21.000Z","msg":"依家仲行緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無巴絲幫手推住Po先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似沉緊"},{"pid":"35a927f5192297c2d8837889c9ced8833078f2ce","tid":684503,"uid":79662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd677a4b90b8f75a1abd86346ca6c80f67fcab20","tid":684503,"uid":188708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c941d05c57e2b61a18ed88a6f855218b6bfbf571","tid":684503,"uid":79662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:05:39.000Z","msg":"巴打我都住米蘭啵 <br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  坐火車都4個鍾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05