,"quote":{"pid":"6c5f6f4e8fc8bb145d9c4e7f562cfab386cfebab","tid":684503,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:46:04.000Z","msg":"橋哥咁快無消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:26:27.000Z","msg":"有啲意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282defc6ebc5fb3f2fe6b3d07baaf3fb7c2a8d95","tid":684503,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19d8b5de8f14d212a9b34b6228223f1e8991dac7","tid":684503,"uid":188708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c5f6f4e8fc8bb145d9c4e7f562cfab386cfebab","tid":684503,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T16:46:04.000Z","msg":"橋哥咁快無消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:26:27.000Z","msg":"有啲意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:30:15.000Z","msg":"好耐無見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae7451f92586e17e884e80ded58966e3db189aa","tid":684503,"uid":66607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8c6e66ce4390c3d651330012c388247fd256d38f","tid":684503,"uid":188708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T14:56:14.000Z","msg":"米蘭去威尼斯話近唔近，話遠唔遠，如果相信Google大神嘅指路行高速公路，大概兩日半就可以行完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/30/225523_fd4a73913a78fc9f2f0061010b36334a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F30%2F225523_fd4a73913a78fc9f2f0061010b36334a.png&h=d9477039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當然實際上就無可能三日啦...Live之前講幾句真心話先，順便交代吓點解想行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一路好欣賞好多人講得出做得到，好有決心去達成目標，而自己就成日婆婆媽媽唔敢去馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上個月去海邊嘅時候，為咗趕得切睇日落，一路狂奔幾百米，就係為咗睇到鹹蛋黃喺山邊落，睇住水嘅顏色連埋個景慢慢變暗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰吓嘅感覺係：好耐無試過咁單純去做一樣嘢，而且想做就去做。<br />\n<br />\n適逢自己喺米蘭Exchange做廢青一年，又有少少假期<br />\n<br />\n唔想自己再廢落去，難得腦裡面閃過呢個念頭，就覺得唔得，唔可以令自己後悔，成廿一歲人，要做返件實現自己嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n威尼斯，曾經係世界上最富裕嘅城邦，喺中世紀以後，呢個地方發明自己嘅規則，好多人去搜尋機會，追尋夢想。行去呢個地方，就好似有種圓夢嘅感覺咁。<br />\n<br />\n- - -<br />\n<br />\n如果要為呢個旅程改個名，我會幻想自己係世界上最出名嘅意大利人&mdash;Mario，係呀紅色衫水管佬，過五關斬六將咁前往城堡拯救公主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n公主我就無喇，城堡都好似無，唯有當終點威尼斯嘅聖馬可教堂係Boss城堡，由米蘭出發，行路去威尼斯，拯救我嘅夢想。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:44:30.000Z","msg":"喺倫敦發來賀電支持下樓主先"},{"pid":"548aa3bc0f315d9947f096c8f65e2a2b4f54fdc6","tid":684503,"uid":188708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:47:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/024710_26113fa3accd515017e5212d5479b843.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F024710_26113fa3accd515017e5212d5479b843.png&h=93527d43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日落但仲有兩個幾鐘先到 腳開始痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbed095a13d71a3ada8bf432094a7acf324b011","tid":684503,"uid":121173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:57:54.000Z","msg":"加油<br />\n支持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414d890c5a7479f9c2d9b7210208bb17e26c255b","tid":684503,"uid":81685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T19:11:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>橋哥咁快無消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>有啲意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有咩意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surpri