class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n詳後"},{"pid":"e23416bb885cc6b6a9f91671d2bf9e4dfb92aa5b","tid":684503,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T22:13:06.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c32c84470e6a80623925500542dc17f66abb7f","tid":684503,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"950a744c4ec86d8ac5afae7dc6ff27e8c3eca429","tid":684503,"uid":16608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T21:06:48.000Z","msg":"Tu sei a Cazzo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T22:16:41.000Z","msg":"*un <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cc59d50e0b7c8fcd5b4d1a905c1cf27fb11dfe6","tid":684503,"uid":188708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"950a744c4ec86d8ac5afae7dc6ff27e8c3eca429","tid":684503,"uid":16608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T21:06:48.000Z","msg":"Tu sei a Cazzo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T22:18:42.000Z","msg":"Non parlo italiano <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6cce2ab1b01e9de796629925e8f5060445b07f","tid":684503,"uid":188708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T22:28:45.000Z","msg":"World 1 - Lombardia<br />\n<br />\nWorld 1-1 Milan-Bergamo(Zanica)<br />\n任務地圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/062538_ebd9c87a4d923735528c4244db1bb81d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F062538_ebd9c87a4d923735528c4244db1bb81d.png&h=de4f74b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n預想長度：53公里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n預想到達時間：21:30<br />\n預想Highlight：<br />\n米蘭大教堂<br />\n威尼斯門（Porta Venezia）<br />\n米蘭地鐵終點站Gessate<br />\nTrezzo鎮絕景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n農田風光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3f2581529b29eb0f023b202acda9369a0721c56","tid":684503,"uid":66607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T22:35:56.000Z","msg":"橋哥最好搵日用熱水浸下全身，同埋拉下筋"},{"pid":"8020ea6ceffa3199413a9f0ecc6e9432195c4150","tid":684503,"uid":188708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T22:55:21.000Z","msg":"今朝遲咗起身，本身打算0930出發，結果搞呢樣嗰樣都係要1030先搞掂曬去到今次旅程嘅起點米蘭大教堂。呢個地方可以話係米蘭（幾乎唯一嘅）地標，座落喺市中心最中間位置。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/064217_6cc45013b3146ef746d63d57d2536756.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F064217_6cc45013b3146ef746d63d57d2536756.png&h=04134235&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n難得Exchange好友相伴，我就提議不如送我去Porta Venezia（Porta Venezia）米蘭從前嘅城市結構好似中國啲城池咁，有好多度門，而城門有好多已經拆曬，淨返少量遺跡被保存。<br />\n由大教堂行20分鐘左右，已經到咗威尼斯門。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/064826_3cec55d105ed59fe7542776650bdba45.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F064826_3cec55d105ed59fe7542776650bdba45.png&h=ac56f4d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朋友都話呢個送別好似係古人送朋友去城門咁，其實都係，一離開米蘭，西出陽關無故人呀。<br />\n<br />\n啲電車幾靚<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/064840_b8c9f555c68b2a2d402d031ea812ee75.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F064840_b8c9f555c68b2a2d402d031ea812ee75.png&h=f4aa2114&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟手食埋個早餐，先同朋友講拜拜，雖然心入面知道好似本身要趕路唔應該食早餐，但嗰陣又覺得行快啲就會趕到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n路過中央車站，見到有車去威尼斯，如果搭火車，四個鐘就到喇屌你，可恥<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/065338_2ead5e6345b631cb0a4d33ca046c5f7a.png[/img\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F065338_2ead5e6345b631cb0a4d33ca046c5f7a.png%5B%2Fimg&d=nXJoC05fDDEosIck8i9fsjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=98f151ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/065338_2ead5e6345b631cb0a4d33ca046c5f7a.png[/img</a><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/065356_28428e008316ad0ab56d8d266896ad52.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F065356_28428e008316ad0ab56d8d266896ad52.png&h=2719d261&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n平時好焦急嘅馬利奧當刻居然唔急，完全唔知後面條路係幾撚長......"},{"pid":"ed83769ab0db18d4b59748c810fccfd1f2ecc048","tid":684503,"uid":188708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T22:57:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/065704_f17f007848e2ac662802f63f70978077.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F065704_f17f007848e2ac662802f63f70978077.png&h=5266687c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64c7b0bc10370102be24c34a23eca4c889ecf48c","tid":684503,"uid":40026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T23:02:13.000Z","msg":"係羅馬支持下樓主！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"745f32ef01d19c23a78354fba72fb994f1b2c699","tid":684503,"uid":188708,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T23:02:48.000Z","msg":"好喇跟著真係行喇<br />\n其實Google平時嘅預想速度係合理，一個鐘頭五公里，行得快應該可以超過呢個數<br />\n但孭住一個10kg嘅背囊，爆發力基本上無咗，頭兩三個鐘狀態算好（雖然唔夠瞓），但都只係Keep到啱啱好5km/h<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/070101_3cbfbf77357150d852a34ae95a6676b6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F070101_3cbfbf77357150d852a34ae95a6676b6.png&h=362f8062&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/070112_f732f7fe1498c874b75759e3fd38078f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F070112_f732f7fe1498c874b75759e3fd38078f.png&h=d2492a94&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/070124_e87cd475b0259882f06413901d2ccee2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F070124_e87cd475b0259882f06413901d2ccee2.png&h=577b787c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/070137_3cb50a3efc48e1e85c91a5c5490d8bfd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F070137_3cb50a3efc48e1e85c91a5c5490d8bfd.png&h=731d1410&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/070145_2865558b48c30500649ebbe1f69d8940.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F070145_2865558b48c30500649ebbe1f69d8940.png&h=8399ec8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行到大概15-20km遠，開始係一片片農田<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/070156_43779178ce85640416039a0fc16a16c3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F070156_43779178ce85640416039a0fc16a16c3.png&h=fce36d3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46d9b9b3199ab7d1b4c91170940c694d4af1128e","tid":684503,"uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T23:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ab66394a43246b01153a76839994e0801ecb07","tid":684503,"uid":160063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"444cf6782ed548b6dc4d4e259e51f9b090f78411","tid":684503,"uid":188708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T20:29:09.000Z","msg":"個意外就係頭先中間無行人路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T23:14:00.000Z","msg":"去到中間你應該日日都會遇到不斷意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0a75c139196d5c115bae697383a9248666dcdc","tid":684503,"uid":188708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T23:18:17.000Z","msg":"中間一路未覺肚餓，可能太熱一路行都唔覺，去到四點幾先坐低食嘢<br />\n嗰陣已經幾攰，畢竟都未試過一日行咁多，嗰陣行到18-19k，已經頭昏腦脹到開呢個Po打錯Title<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n接近六點，終於行到米蘭地鐵嘅尾站Gessate，但因為已經發覺無乜時間，無兜過去影相，只係影咗間超市<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/070748_63de100ca696797d19a03d3a901776a8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F070748_63de100ca696797d19a03d3a901776a8.png&h=c9393f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n超市名叫Esselunga，個人會譯佢做長江（肛），明嘅就明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身一路沿住古運河行，都唔需要點諗，所以覺得應該9點幾可以行到<br />\n點知Google Map話行得嗰條路係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/071030_8e0a4970698ee73ae0012dd75f3f24ef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F071030_8e0a4970698ee73ae0012dd75f3f24ef.png&h=cc31db52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n轉彎之後直情唔得閒影相，CLS啲大貨車都會行呢條路，而佢根本係無行人路<br />\n但又真係好似無其他路（一係就落返一路行嘅單車徑，但佢根本唔係佢Zanica呢邊，行嗰邊隨時要兜多十公里以上....）...<br />\n面對一邊係可能會俾車撞嘅公路，另一邊係農田雜草，我好快就選擇咗投入雜草嘅懷抱<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/071409_db50e237b8b68696d8d8e771095dbd3b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F071409_db50e237b8b68696d8d8e771095dbd3b.png&h=cc865823&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n頭十幾分鐘簡直就好似去探險咁，係我又著長襪先頂硬上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/071422_e1345d8a8b7a9943d510dc1c4c3f92f9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F071422_e1345d8a8b7a9943d510dc1c4c3f92f9.png&h=b27d73b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/071428_41e42e203925287df592935ac4c9ad12.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F071428_41e42e203925287df592935ac4c9ad12.png&h=c48f832e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/071443_b705a8f055eb635fd3b0e0bd9254feca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F071443_b705a8f055eb635fd3b0e0bd9254feca.png&h=a4ad2f49&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/071457_c245ad1519aa9ae21f5198258eea73a6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F071457_c245ad1519aa9ae21f5198258eea73a6.png&h=87141673&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身Google話半個鐘嘅路程，就係咁用咗成個鐘有多，仲要成鞋都係泥，成腳都係草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後見到個有返行人路嘅路牌有啲感動，但我又諗，吖原來你真係知係需要行人路呢樣嘢嘅咩...."},{"pid":"adbdef91a326178e077bfc12aac68e7e054e3c3e","tid":684503,"uid":188708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7ab66394a43246b01153a76839994e0801ecb07","tid":684503,"uid":160063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"444cf6782ed548b6dc4d4e259e51f9b090f78411","tid":684503,"uid":188708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T20:29:09.000Z","msg":"個意外就係頭先中間無行人路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T23:14:00.000Z","msg":"去到中間你應該日日都會遇到不斷意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T23:19:31.000Z","msg":"Google街景同衛星係我嘅朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一陣再Check吓聽日條路到底係咪行得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca87c289198861bffa6acf7445610161813b80a","tid":684503,"uid":188708,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T23:32:12.000Z","msg":"終於行返正常行人路，然後望一望天，哇頂已經開始黃昏<br />\n即刻Check到底仲要行幾耐，個預測係四個幾鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要係中間好似有啲唔會行得嘅公路<br />\n而自己行到20幾公里又開始攰，隻腳開始痛，特別係小腿以下<br />\n<br />\n我就知道，由於自己遲出發同埋一開始太慢，根本無可能入黑前（9點鐘日落，9點半基本上黑曬）抵達目的地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我就Check巴士啦，係可以搭前少少，慳返一個鐘多少少，但會去到Zanica或者附近城鎮嘅巴士，七點已經係尾班車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n意大利交通網絡真係不撚得了，可能佢地全部都覺得，一個人要依賴交通工具連可憐都唔值得可憐<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/072636_f7c3fb292a67f5499825c8e5554ed654.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F072636_f7c3fb292a67f5499825c8e5554ed654.png&h=bd118449&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n夜晚行唔知係車路定行人路嘅地方真係唔得掂，天氣預報仲話夜晚行雷<br />\n咁面子緊要定命仔緊要吖，都要上車㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搭咗三四個字就到咗Trezzo，本身諗住七點會行到嘅地方<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/072938_126eb7d14e9139f98be02b9bd27ed8b8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F072938_126eb7d14e9139f98be02b9bd27ed8b8.png&h=6d2cd83d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/073009_7682d320daee749e0bb2497613ef9eb5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F073009_7682d320daee749e0bb2497613ef9eb5.png&h=761c0850&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/073021_9a3e8ae5a847b113d29d28ef5ada8060.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F073021_9a3e8ae5a847b113d29d28ef5ada8060.png&h=070d58cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/073035_25fcfb7ecc8266cd4de3a51105a8857f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F073035_25fcfb7ecc8266cd4de3a51105a8857f.png&h=25ee9c0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係好靚，眼睇仲靚，嗰吓我嘩咗出聲<br />\n覺得好似行咗咁多個鐘，見到呢個景就抵返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab050e9c8fb2735592d4087b921c300b8cdd1bf8","tid":684503,"uid":188708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T23:39:34.000Z","msg":"但係呢<br />\n咁靚，係因為就嚟日落吖嘛<br />\n古人寫得出「夕陽無限好，只是近黃昏」，背後對黃昏咁感嘆，可能因為佢都成日做行路撚，知道入黑就大檸樂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/073422_c1c1b24138101886679303614492890c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F073422_c1c1b24138101886679303614492890c.png&h=13b89f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過山車起俾邊個玩呀荒山野嶺<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/073447_700a71b682aa8c0e070fc27fef5922e8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F073447_700a71b682aa8c0e070fc27fef5922e8.png&h=e0105f34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來附近有要渣車先去到嘅Commercial Complex（我估得我係咁樣行過去） <br />\n食Lunch嘅時候已經無Pasta嗰啲，得包，無食字邊，所以唔飽<br />\n所以趕路都要醫肚，麥當勞是窮撚的朋友，兩個包加個朱古力奶昔都係3.4歐羅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/073508_0bde7d58c7ab1a999f09d3be4829016f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F073508_0bde7d58c7ab1a999f09d3be4829016f.png&h=d81ccb85&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/073520_9458e31c03cfddc93b772000973b2f52.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F073520_9458e31c03cfddc93b772000973b2f52.png&h=9d8c7061&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇住個天越來越黑，我都真心越來越驚，驚行到Zanica已經無得Check in，驚路況未必行到，又驚自己對腳未必捱到..."},{"pid":"07db329a6b53e692babb1de5fb092aa9832a999f","tid":684503,"uid":145730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T23:47:30.000Z","msg":"留名支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8267c9fef749e7374ce0b26673c51a452a0a0e","tid":684503,"uid":188708,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T23:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/074033_a2f340cfb3640c29987371650cb41e8a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F074033_a2f340cfb3640c29987371650cb41e8a.png&h=674eccdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n晚上九點半，天已經深藍，而要行有行人路嘅地方，Google話我知仲有兩個鐘多少少，而我對腳已經話我知自己無可能Keep到5km/h，行到3.5km/h都偷笑<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/074044_066ceb7c533d1fbc31f389a8fbaaa61d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F074044_066ceb7c533d1fbc31f389a8fbaaa61d.png&h=aeaf95a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行行吓見到墳場，覺得其實死咗都幾好，好似幾安詳<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後個天有真係開始有少少雲間閃電<br />\n呢個狀態我真係就崩潰，如果當時有的士經過，就算收我三四十歐，我都好可能會上車，奈何連的士都見唔到<br />\n<br />\n然後我見到附近有 火 車 站 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/074056_0ad547a7e008013be3c8cd0579366617.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F074056_0ad547a7e008013be3c8cd0579366617.png&h=938829af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上咗往Bergamo嘅區間車，雖然其實唔會近啲，但至少Bergamo都算大城市，有的士嘅機會大啲，就算無，Bergamo都有Hostel可以住，雖然我本來住Zanica嘅訂金就會凍過水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/074118_a028fcdd0f42c902a5be46fa5e67d138.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F074118_a028fcdd0f42c902a5be46fa5e67d138.png&h=11420bc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我衰，我搭咗車....但我就算搭咗車，都係有條仆街健步如飛咁去搭咗最後一架的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後車站附近嘅黑人同埋意大利人都問我係咪要Taxi，呢吓我雖然有少少淆底，但都問佢幾錢，佢話15歐羅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實好貴，但我睇Uber去Zanica要20幾，算啦，硬食<br />\n（唔記得講價<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"64cab884cd86b0e5dd17a9f6a02969881796b028","tid":684503,"uid":188708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T23:56:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/074144_d9312e0b8c1993593c4361820b0da8c5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F074144_d9312e0b8c1993593c4361820b0da8c5.png&h=4041426e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n夜晚十一點正，<br />\n屌<br />\n你<br />\n老<br />\n母<br />\n終<br />\n於<br />\n到<br />\n咗<br />\n<br />\n有自己房，連埋早餐都係25歐羅，算係咁<br />\n不過自己預算真係有啲差，聽朝都係睇清楚有咩路可以行先行...<br />\n<br />\n今日以上，有咩聽日再講，再唔瞓聽日無力行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d2fa9313278d37b360081cb8a622c9483f43918","tid":684503,"uid":188708,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T23:57:36.000Z","msg":"多謝大家留名支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我會汲取今日教訓㗎喇，盡量都唔會再搭車"},{"pid":"1d8eb16ca124087939af019c7ba6f03337d3798c","tid":684503,"uid":47202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T00:12:39.000Z","msg":"加油, 希望唔好爛尾"},{"pid":"1b7bb847bc3f9cafd55db9d3f2